Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Los Gatos, CA
Description: My hometown where I lived for 18 years! All of my childhood friends and my immediate family live here still so I visit often.

Name: Lochcarron, Scotland
Description: A tiny village where my mother was born and where many of my relatives live. It is a small fishing village and one of my favorite places in the world.

Name: Truckee, CA
Description: A town near Lake Tahoe where my family spends most holidays. It is really warm in the summer but most well known for skiing in the winter.

Name: Mae Sariang, Thailand
Description: A village in Thailand that I visited 4 years ago. This trip to Thailand was my first solo travel adventure.

Name: St. Andrews, Scotland
Description: A seaside town near where some of my family lives. I visit often when I am in the UK and love looking at the castle ruins.
